{"name":"Rando","tagline":"","body":"<html><button onclick = dieRoll() style=\"background-color:red\" >Roll A Die</button>\r\n<p id = \"dieRoll\">Die result will appear here</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<button onclick = coinToss() style=\"background-color:lightgreen\" >Toss A Coin</button>\r\n<p id = \"coinToss\">Coin toss result will appear here</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<button onclick = diceRoll() style=\"background-color:yellow\" >Roll 2 Dice</button>\r\n<p id = \"diceRoll\">2 Dice Sum will appear here</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<button onclick = pickCard() style=\"background-color:lightblue\" >Pick a Card</button>\r\n<p id = \"pickCard\">Card result will appear here</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<script>\r\nfunction dieRoll(){\r\n\r\nvar roll = Math.floor((Math.random() * 6) + 1);\r\ndocument.getElementById(\"dieRoll\").innerHTML =\"Die Result: \" + roll;}\r\n\r\nfunction diceRoll(){\r\n\r\nvar roll1 = Math.floor((Math.random() * 6) + 1);\r\nvar roll2 = Math.floor((Math.random() * 6) + 1);\r\nvar rollSum = (roll1+roll2);\r\ndocument.getElementById(\"diceRoll\").innerHTML =\"2 Dice sum: \" + rollSum;}\r\n\r\n\r\nfunction coinToss(){\r\n\r\n\r\nvar toss = Math.floor((Math.random() * 2));\r\nif(toss === 1){\r\ntoss = \"heads\";}\r\nelse{\r\ntoss = \"tails\";} document.getElementById(\"coinToss\").innerHTML =\"Coin Result :\" + toss;}\r\n\r\nfunction pickCard(){\r\nvar suits = [\"Spade\", \"Club\", \"Heart\", \"Diamond\"];\r\nvar cardNos = [\"Ace\", \"Two\", \"Three\", \"Four\", \"Five\", \"Six\", \"Seven\", \"Eight\", \"Nine\", \"Ten\", \"Jack\", \"Queen\", \"King\"];\r\nvar x = Math.floor((Math.random() * 4));\r\nvar y = Math.floor((Math.random() * 13));\r\nvar a = cardNos[y];\r\nvar b = suits[x];\r\ndocument.getElementById(\"pickCard\").innerHTML = a + \" of \" + b;\r\n}\r\n\r\n       \r\n         </script>\r\n         \r\n        </html>","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}